window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A number-one <i>New York Times</i> best-selling author, Charlaine Harris penned the addictive Sookie Stackhouse series. In <i>Day Shift</i> psychic Manfred Bernardo is hounded by the press after a client drops dead during a reading. Turning to the local vampire's lover for help, Manfred hopes she can put the squeeze on the scandal before someone else is put on ice. </p>"; 
